      "role": "user",
      "content": "interesting. so if the moisture is too high it basically just stalls the process. what about the specific types of sugars? does it matter if i'm using glucose vs fructose or something? i just want to be really specific for my notes on how the structure of the sugar affects the speed of the reaction.",
